Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把关东煮的泡撇掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的工作就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干脆别当神了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧去收容所吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是客户委托的重要工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有夜班人员 店长会很烦恼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛 好烫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么只有我老遇到这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别进来啊 你这只穷神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫对我的神明都做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正义的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你大黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有正版的授权擅自命名的 你这黑心商户
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个店名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种店不是一抓一大把嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦 摸摸我啦小日和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让小日和带我们来这里的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然能找到这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是根据夜卜的味…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可说不出口的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话从你口说出来可充满了犯罪的气味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底干麻来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们那收到个与我们无关的委托所以转给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你闲的要命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜 你的脸色有点差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又没吃饭么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会觉得我偷了钱吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的这么想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连神都认为我无可救药了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是死了是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音...你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的委托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小福 大黑 店就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 交给我是什么意思哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共582日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱除上井杜町上空出现的的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是单纯的委托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢 风穴大开之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各分社肯定大量收到了这样的委托了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音他...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟妖怪只能用神器才能斩除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有无神器就天壤之别了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 但要说的不是这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么说才好...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要做个了结了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还是赶快结果了他比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日 日和 你在做什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在  在...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有或无  他并不是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音就是雪音 不是作为神器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是像对待人一样 好好的和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有双漂亮的眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在风中摇摆的山查子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这个果实连鸟儿都不吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不甜也不苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽无毒 但也于身体无益
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无用处 空荡荡的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被任何鸟儿啄上一口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就悄然退色 无所牵连 干瘪后消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个可怜的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野良 你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像以前那样多多使用我吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡道的东西...不管是什么我都会巧妙的帮你斩掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪音 别去听野良的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是...那个东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丰苇中国　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引起骚动之物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾夜卜神自天降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臣服于雪器威严之下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潇清种种污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩不掉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然变钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来被雪音刺得就够受的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净化的水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野良 你给我滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这家伙是个不正经的臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是我找到 给他取的名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪器 由我来磨练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被甩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长年陪伴身边的绯之名...在哭泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫雪音的坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快处理的话 夜卜会死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜...会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜卜 刚才把你扔出去了真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.21,0:24:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才应该要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们和好的证明 接受吧
